accd (0.2.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix 0x28 session_mgr_state first byte to session_index (not phase).
  * Variable-length per-session records matching exe FUN_140035130.
  * Fix 7-slot schedule layout matching Kunos wire capture: session end
    at slot 4, overtime at slot 5 (was off by one).
  * Per-connection 0x28 build with client clock base (FUN_1400418b0).
  * Re-broadcast 0x28 on phase transitions.
  * Enable per-peer timestamp adjustment in 0x1e/0x39 relay using
    client-to-client pong deltas for correct dead-reckoning.
  * Compute 0x28 schedule timestamps as absolute client game clock
    values matching exe formula (ts - server_now + client_ts + RTT/2).

