accd (0.1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Handshake validated against real Kunos accServer.exe 1.10.2.
  * Fix reject response to use 0x0c format (was 0x0b with 0xFFFF).
  * Fix accept header to include UDP port (was protocol version).
  * Fix welcome trailer strings to use u16-byte-len UTF-8 (was Format-A).
  * Fix CarInfo field order: raceNumber before carModel.
  * Parse DriverInfo and CarInfo from handshake request body.
  * Populate full welcome trailer with all Kunos sub-records.
  * Add post-accept 0x28, 0x36, 0x37, 0x4e welcome sequence.
  * Fix weather broadcast: correct scaling factors and grip level field.
  * Fix weather_init called from config with event.json values.
  * Preserve ambient/track temp across session reset.
  * Write results on session_advance for the last session.
  * Fix server-full off-by-one (nconns already includes connecting client).
  * Wire BanList into Server struct: enforce bans in handshake, persist on /ban.
  * Fix json_free for string-rooted documents.
  * Add systemd service to RPM package.
  * Harden systemd service with sandboxing directives.
  * Remove unused monitor_push_welcome_sequence.

